Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4 5…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用数也知道吧
